Taking Action and Preparing for the Future

Tuseday, April 28, 2020       10:00 am ET / 7:00 am PT.        With Sarah Smith

Register Now














What you'll learn:

  • How to prepare for âcourageous conversationsâ when itâs time to return to the office

About Sarah Smith

Sarah Smith is an award-winning professional communicator with a passion for driving strong performance from the inside out. As President and owner of Premium Communication, Sarah builds strategic internal communication, engagement, branding, and transformational change plans that enable, engage, and empower employees to deliver business results.







About ContactMonkey

ContactMonkey is an internal communications and employee engagement tracking solution that integrates into Outlook and Gmail inboxes. We built our tool to help internal communicators transform employee newsletters into a two-way communication channel.
Use ContactMonkey to create, send, track, and measure employee feedback and the effectiveness of your corporate communications.
